minios-session-manager (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * CLI interface for session management
  * GTK3 GUI interface that calls CLI operations
  * Support for viewing, creating, activating, deleting, and cleaning up sessions
  * Full support for all three session modes: native, dynfilefs, and raw
  * Filesystem compatibility detection and mode restrictions
  * Size specification support for dynfilefs and raw modes
  * DynFileFS integration with automatic file splitting
  * Compatible with both JSON and legacy session formats
  * Comprehensive documentation with compatibility matrix

 -- MiniOS Team <team@minios.dev>  Mon, 05 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000